SUMMARY:Supply Chain Security Deep Dive
DESCRIPTION:Microsoft Reactor Toronto\nA focused deep dive into modern sup
 ply chain security\, exploring how artifact attestations\, virtual registr
 ies\, and SLSA compliance work together to establish trust\, integrity\, a
 nd traceability across the software lifecycle.\n\nThis session is a part o
 f a series! Learn more **[here](https://developer.microsoft.com/reactor/se
 ries/S-1311/?wt.mc_id=meetup_S-1311_webpage_reactor)**
