SUMMARY:The Future of AI in Microsoft Fabric: Data Agents and Beyond
DESCRIPTION:Microsoft Reactor Toronto\nThe first session in the FabCon and
  SQLCon recap series will will cover how Fabric brings AI to your data usi
 ng interoperable Data Agents that work across the AI ecosystem to unlock d
 eeper insights.\n\nYou'll also learn how AI-powered data engineering and d
 ata science capabilities help teams create intelligent\, enterprise-ready 
 solutions.\n\n📍 This session is a part of a series. [Learn more here](h
 ttps://developer.microsoft.com/reactor/series/S-1660/?wt.mc_id=meetup_S-16
 60_webpage_reactor)
